summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 5576, entitled: "An Ordinance providing for the laying off, extending and establishing of Woodland Avenue, in the City of Seattle, from the Supplemental Plat of Woodland Park Addition to connect with said Avenue in Windell's Division of Green Lake Addition, and providing for the condemnation of real estate necessary therefor," approved the 18th day of October, 1899.
